column5: For the first time in 15 years I have a clean shaven face, it's all for a good cause ... I know for a fact that some very active board members like myself have suffered or are suffering and battling some sort reproductive cancer. Will you donate ? Will you participate ? Maybe we should start an OFC Wolfpack ?  http://ca.movember.com/mospace/8025525
This my 4th year and I donate every time to Cancer society. Mo's unite!
I've had a stach for 45 years and it's not coming off....but donations have been made as always.

I've had a stach for 45 years and it's not coming off....but donations have been made as always.  Same hey Lew; but you working as a fireman, have no doubt singed it off a couple of times.
